<emphasis id="65BBEA84FFD1FFC1FAAFFC966AE2E3EC" box="[1339,1450,877,910]" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">Habitat.</emphasis>
[Lowland tropical forest.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="1FD5651DFFD1FFC1FAAFFC6E6999E3BF" pageId="4" pageNumber="309" type="food_feeding">
<paragraph id="57703696FFD1FFC1FAAFFC6E6999E3BF" blockId="4.[1338,2545,724,1502]" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">
<emphasis id="65BBEA84FFD1FFC1FAAFFC6E6905E3D4" box="[1339,1613,917,950]" pageId="4" pageNumber="309">Food and Feeding.</emphasis>
The Golden-white Bare-ear Marmoset eats small fruits, nectar, gums, and small animal prey.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
